results.name: Square array A(g,h) = 1 if combinatorial game g has value greater than or equal to that of game h, otherwise 0, listed antidiagonally in order A(0,0), A(1,0), A(0,1), A(2,0), A(1,1), A(0,2), ...
comment: Here we use the encoding explained in A106486. A(i,j) = A(A106485(j),A106485(i)).
link: A. Karttunen, Scheme-program for computing this sequence.
xref: Row 0 is the characteristic function of A126001 (shifted one step) and similarly, column 0 is the characteristic function of A126002. Cf. tables A126010 and A126000.
results.author: _Antti Karttunen_, Dec 18 2006
